---
// One idea: speed is the whole game. Big animated stat.
---
<section class="problem section" aria-labelledby="problem-h" data-orchestrate>
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <p class="kicker reveal">The leak in your funnel</p>
    <h2 id="problem-h" class="problem-h reveal">
      <span class="big" data-count data-to="65" data-suffix="%">65%</span>
      of businesses take over a day to answer a DM.
    </h2>
    <p class="problem-sub reveal">
      By then the lead has messaged three competitors and bought from whoever replied first.
      You did not lose the sale on price or product. You lost it on silence.
      DMClosed answers in seconds, every time, on every channel.
    </p>
    <div class="problem-bars reveal" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="bar">
        <span class="bar-label">You, replying by hand</span>
        <span class="bar-track"><span class="bar-fill bar-slow" data-bar></span></span>
        <span class="bar-val">~14 hrs</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bar">
        <span class="bar-label">DMClosed</span>
        <span class="bar-track"><span class="bar-fill bar-fast" data-bar></span></span>
        <span class="bar-val">4 sec</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem { text-align: center; }
  .problem .kicker { margin-bottom: 1.1rem; }
  .problem-h { font-size: var(--step-3); line-height: 1.05; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .problem-h .big {
    display: block; font-size: var(--step-5); color: var(--primary-hi);
    line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }
  /* the stat lands with a little extra weight when revealed */
  html.has-motion .problem-h .big {
    transform: scale(0.9); transform-origin: center bottom;
    transition: transform 1.1s var(--ease-out-quint);
  }
  html.has-motion .problem-h.is-in .big { transform: scale(1); }
  .problem-sub { font-size: var(--step-1); color: var(--ink-2); max-width: 56ch; margin-inline: auto; line-height: 1.55; }

  .problem-bars { margin-top: 3rem; display: grid; gap: 1.1rem; max-width: 560px; margin-inline: auto; text-align: left; }
  .bar { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .bar-label { font-size: var(--step--1); color: var(--muted); font-weight: 500; }
  .bar-track { height: 14px; border-radius: var(--radius-pill); background: var(--surface); overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--line-soft); }
  .bar-fill { display: block; height: 100%; border-radius: var(--radius-pill); width: 0; }
  .bar-slow { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--surface-hi), var(--muted)); }
  .bar-fast { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-strong), var(--accent-strong)); box-shadow: 0 0 18px -2px var(--glow-amber); }
  .bar-val { font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; font-size: var(--step-1); }
  .bar:first-child .bar-val { color: var(--muted); }
  .bar:last-child .bar-val { color: var(--accent-hi); }
</style>
